Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, as indistinguishable from a woman as a butterfly is from a flower, {no idea what is really going on in this flower-butterfly trickery}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived to help Benio, but unknowingly only caused her more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if someone exposes his disguise, \Nthey would both be in dire straits;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so as they observe Shinobu giggling ominously, they can't help wondering if their game is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Following the law of "the older, the wiser," \Nthe Count promptly sees through Ranmaru's cover,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,turning things from bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when Benio seizes the moment to cut the Gordian Knot and forcefully dispel all doubts. {not a single word but seems to be talking about some historical kabuki play}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to enter the bath with Lady Benio and rub her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are, with troubles piling up one after another!{さもあらばあれ重ね重ねの大ピンチ}
