Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That was an awfully close call, Ranmaru.{酷い目に遭っちゃったわね蘭丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you at least glad that they didn't blow my cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. That's what happens \Nwhen you rush things. {さすがになってしまう焦っちゃったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Lady Benio.{失礼しますべにお様}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the Count asks if you would like to join him for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Benio.{おやすみなさいbenioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ranmaru, do you have a room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We've got a room just for us, three maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Three of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you need to be extra careful with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry,{平気平気}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left now is to go to sleep as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. Today went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, with his habitual...{いつもの通りいつもの愛用の}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,lily loincloth?!{花柄の越中 - 越中 stands for 越中ふんどし, loincloth / flower-patterned }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru! \NAh, I let it slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko! Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy.{りっぱ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, do you need help with something?{Benio様何かご用ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's nothing important.{あいや別に大したようでは}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let us take care \Nof our new friend Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was she so panicked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make me some grilled chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here. High beds aren't suited for people who turn in their sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ranmaru tosses while sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranmaru, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master...\NYoung Master...{若様若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why?{えどうして}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think they won't notice that?{それがみんなにバレずに済むと思うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,G-G-Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.\NWe'll move your things tomorrow morning.{荷物は明日の朝取りに来ればいいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting to sleep in the same room as Benio...\NI'm such a happy man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get down from the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be my territory here, \Nand your territory there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? If you breach this border, \NI won't let it slide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure thing. \NWell, goodnight, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mh, it's so bright...{眩しいなぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, are you awake yet?{紅緒さんそろそろ起きない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you were here, Lady Benio.{ああべにおさまこんなところに}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko, why are you giving me that kind of look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio used to be such a late riser...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this is happening.{僕信じられないな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, what is it you're doing here?{benio様何をしてるのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing? \NWhat does it look like? I'm sweeping.{何よって見ればわかるでしょお掃除よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Masters should delegate this kind of work to their subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you have maids in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to have some general idea of what our numerous servants' work is like.{でも(おおせ?)の方向に(乗せる)ことも - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lady Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who gave that order?{誰がそんな命令を}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember it, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she makes me do this out of spite,{でも別に意地悪してるわけじゃないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that woman is just devoted to her duties.{あの人は職務に忠実なだけよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll give her a piece of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, why be so vindictive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? \NWasn't making a mess of this place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your original goal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.{おはよう皆さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.{良いできですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who arranged this flower?{この花は誰がいけました}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?{誰がいけたのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, I...{あの私が}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It doesn't resemble your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So as I was saying, I ordered Ranko to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you arrange all the vases here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done an excellent job.{出来栄えは見事です}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds about right. Ahem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you did something unnecessary!{しかし余計なことをしてくれましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep doing it for Lady Benio, \Nshe'll never learn herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow morning on, refrain from unnecessary actions! Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Ranko for it, so I'm to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault for answering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you must abide\Nby your own roles. Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a loose thread on your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There, I cut it. \NSorry for the holdup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.{ご苦労}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so careless! \NHow disgraceful of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you'll learn how to compose haiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By mixing simple and transient, \Nwith enough practice, you can even reach the zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the essence of haiku.{俳句の真髄でございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a poem by Matsuo Basho.{芭蕉の(おきな?)も読みました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Frogs jump; \Nwater splashes; \Nold pond." {made it more haiku-like}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of his best known haikus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, my pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,... for this reason ...{でありますからして}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wrote one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Old pond; \Nold hag jumps; \Nsplashes all over; \Nfourth line."{/It's a long meter.}{字余り}{I think it's just a fancy word ran adds to parody kisaragi's educative airs, it means something like "my haiku has extra syllables in it/nonstandard rhythmic pattern"\Nit'd go "It's a stanza" because basically nobody knows what it is anyway\Nso nobody would call us out for saying something that doesn't make sense in subs \Nor better yet, any buzzword from this page https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foot_(prosody)#Disyllables ; on second thought he might just be adding that as a part of the haiku itself so that it fits into a meter, think "bottom text"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with my enormous experience \Nof posing as a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the way women's clothing is \Nstill doesn't rock my boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, there's no one around, \Nso here's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... This must be men's heaven.{これぞ男の快感おわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Mrs. Kisaragi, you look ghastly!\NDon't you need some rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She... She's taking a—{tachishou - piss on the go/in a man's fashion/while standing}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a special massage just for such cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{I hate this}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I swear I just saw that Ranko \Nrelieving herself like a man.{確かにあの蘭子と有名と太刀}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be real! It's too disgusting.\NI need to collect myself.{まさか、そんなおぞましい. 冷静にならねば}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Lady Benio came here, I've been feeling more and more worn out.{ともかくbenio様が来てからというもの少々疲れ気味なのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my roses, always a welcome sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've bloomed wonderfully \Nwith the proper upkeep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, th-that's where...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, stay away!{殿様いけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why should I stay away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She just... \NRelieved herself here! No! {/took a man's/standing piss}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You've been acting weird recently.{お前この頃少しおかしいぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go see a doctor if that helps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I assure you, you needn't \Nconcern yourself with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a fine smell!{いい匂い}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless...{これあかんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, can't you be a little more careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just answered nature's call.{自然の呼び声に応えただけだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Boss?{どうしたんです親分?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, you need to follow at least some basic etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, can you hear what you're saying?\NThe reason we all came here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was to break your engagement as soon as possible, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Isn't that right, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, let's not hold back and raise all hell \Nto get the boot in the shortest term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah! Truth be told, I've been itching for action like mad, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There, see? What better time will we have to put our plan into action?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't avoid the unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The best way to go about the farewell show \Nis doing it with one big flashy bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. If it came to this, \Nwe might as well go medieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Attaboy! Let's put our backs into it and level this place in record time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! I'm so glad I can count on you, Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your Huckleberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu... So this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? That sound...{あの音は}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:16.90,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H10121D&\3c&H7BC1D1&}Boss Hanamura Benio's Dwelling{花村紅緒親分御宿所}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm done.{よーしできたこれでよーし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you come up with this time?{お前はまた何を始めたんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it look like? It's a signboard. \NA signboard, cantcha see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's the meaning of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, the whole world will know \Nwhere to find Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't the only one!{これだけじゃないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, lemme show you. Here!{ほら所}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for her personal chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.12,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H10121D&\3c&H7BC1D1&}Boss Hanamura Benio's Bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is for the lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H10121D&\3c&H7BC1D1&}Boss Hanamura Benio's Toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You unruly brute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Just kidding, just kidding!{いや冗談冗談}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, you know a thing or two about style, Mrs. Kisaragi! I really like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!{黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave immediately!{とっとと立ち去りなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you're so scary!{いや怖い怖い}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Making a fool of me!{己,人をバカにして}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll chop your head off!{その首をギザギザにしてやる}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Time to skedaddle! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.85,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you shouldn't be swinging that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss was right, messing with that grandma is always a load of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoundrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! {likely another onore}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't stopping! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You villain! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{>_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you skunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell! \NI ain't losing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it come to this?{どうなってんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi, what in the world happened?{如月どうしましたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are bloodshot, \Nwhat is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just that...{いやそれがその}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! What do you need that for?{もう何ですかそれは}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No reason.{いいえ何でもありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you need some rest, Kisaragi?{少し疲れてるのではありませんかkisaragi}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjusting to all the changes in our way of life caused \Nby Benio's arrival was probably exhausting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, something this trifling wouldn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're making steady progress in Lady Benio's education.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. That is most relieving to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange. That must be Tenmaru and Chimaru barking, and it comes from inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Did something \Njust sweep through the corridor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...{あの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyesight is rather poor these days, \Nwhat did it look like?{そなたはどうです}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... That was... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Mistress hitched the dogs \Nto the rickshaw! {not sure which word to use, maybe harness}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi! Hang on! Kisaragi! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.{なるほどなるほど}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain appears strained. \NActually, I see considerable overall exhaustion. {no idea what meaning of https://jisho.org/word/%E8%85%90%E3%82%8B this is}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs to rest for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.38,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she really make it out okay?{本当に大丈夫かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:52.13,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I'm so worried!{心配だわー}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\NWell, take care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We finished that hag off!{ついあのばあさんやっつけた}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already hear them \Nsending you home, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... I'll have to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home...{うちに帰る}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to live without seeing Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll cut all ties between Shinobu and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll become strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Why am I having such thoughts now? \NI never intended to stay here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...{まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that Benio...{まさか紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek! Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! You can't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kisaragi, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Young Master.\NI apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaragi, I heard you collapsed.{Kisaragiさん倒れたんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing you should \Nconcern yourself with, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be ashamed to be seen in such shape.{お見苦しいところを目にかけまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't overwork yourself, \Nmy irreplaceable Nanny. {/elderly maid/maid supervisor}{baaya by shinobu is "master housekeeper" and baaya by Benio is "wet nanny"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take better care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I don't deserve such words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to take breaks sometimes, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what Mrs. Kisaragi is to Shinobu\Nis about the same as what my Nanny is to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we overdid it a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tea.{お茶をお持ちしました}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, your pads moved to your back \Nand are now vertical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-{\alpha&HFF}Be-Be-Be-Be-Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-Be-{\alpha&HFF}Be-Be-Be-Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.65,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-Be-Be-{\alpha&HFF}Be-Be-Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-Be-Be-Be-{\alpha&HFF}Be-Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-Be-Be-Be-Be-{\alpha&HFF}Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be-Be-Be-Be-Be-Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What did you say, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone see through your disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm dead sure! \NHe just called me Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Called it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But why didn't he tell everyone yet?{でもどうしてみんなに話さないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew all along that I let you, a boy, stay so close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that we sleep and wake up \Nin the same room every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He also knows full well that Ranmaru loves me, \Nwhich means my fidelity might be at risk every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet he was never worried about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't care less about me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me not;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me not;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me not;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me not;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He loves me not...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers are scattering \Nand delusions are intensifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is a sailboat of reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Invincible in battle, High Collar Lady\Njust proved powerless against love ruminations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to understand Shinobu's feelings,{少尉の心の底を測りかねて}\Nour restless High Collar Lady{思い悩むはいからさんに}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,stumbles across a trio of thugs.{突如襲ったらくれ者さんに}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the heat of the moment,{腹立ちまぎれにお相手すると}\Nnone of them realizes that she is unmatched in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always quick to draw her weapon \Nand show off that tomboyish two-handed fencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, geisha Kichiji, \Nwho's in love with Shinobu, appears.{そんなところに少尉に熱い思いを寄せる芸者基地が現れた}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "Here Comes the High Collar Lady":
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Bewildered Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
Comment: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED start}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.88,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.67,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.59,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart;\N I want him to turn around before he leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,20,,to give me that loving glance once again
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have these unrequited feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.74,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.93,Default,,0,0,20,,Just a tomboyish lady who's a little pretentious
